      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS VINCENZA (2) scored at the first run back from a spell last start over 2130m at this track on June 16, finishing 2.75 metres ahead of her rivals. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Meets a comparable field so she can certainly make it two on the bounce this time in work. SALSAWITHSIERRA (1) was out of the money last start when 13 metres from the winner in seventh over 2242m at Narrogin. Best form reference might be her win here three starts back. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. It doesn't get any easier but on her best form she is good enough to take this out. GO JACK CROCKER (4) is on the radar after his last-start fifth over 2242m at Narrogin four days ago. MAJESTIC REALE (3) is in the mix at his first run since scoring over 2185m at Pinjarra eight months ago. Can run a race while fresh.",
